raw_data.description: A Christian based coffee shop located in Hemby Bridge.

reviews_data.review_text: Went to Psalms today with my wife and baby. Such a pleasant Christian café! We enjoyed a latte, a frappuccino, and a Danish pastry. The coffee is flavorful and the baristas along with the owner are super friendly. The atmosphere inside is warm and nicely done, and there’s even a kids’ play area outside. Parking is easy with plenty of gravel spots plus a paved handicap space. My wife and I will definitely be back. They also sell Psalm-branded shirts and have a prayer wall where you can lift others up or share your own needs and blessings. And while you’re there, whether working or chatting, you’ll be surrounded by uplifting worship music.
The perfect coffee shop for the area! So beautiful inside, clean, fresh & very comfy. The girls working are so sweet & the coffee is amazing.
Amazing coffee! They have a lot of options and some snacks as well. I love how there is a fenced in kids play area out front too!
